9) Grade of JONES

**Aim: To find salary grade of JONES.** \
Requirement: Employee + salgrade tables.\
Theory: Join using salary range.\
Query:

SELECT s.grade
FROM employee e
JOIN salgrade s
ON e.sal BETWEEN s.losal AND s.hisal
WHERE e.ename = 'JONES';
